import { StyleSheet } from 'react-native';
import { View, Text } from 'react-native';
export default function Community() {
    return (
        <View style={communityStyles.community}>
            <View style={communityStyles.commBox}>
                <View style={communityStyles.Rectangle8} />
                <View style={communityStyles.Rectangle10} />
                <Svg id='Line2' />
            </View>
            <Text style={communityStyles.JoinusLogin}>
                Join usLogin
            </Text>
            <View style={communityStyles.SearchBar51}>
                <Svg id='Vector' />
                <Svg id='Vector' />
                <Svg id='Vector' />
                <Svg id='Vector' />
            </View>
            <View style={communityStyles['321']}>
                <Svg id='Vector' />
                <Svg id='Vector' />
                <Svg id='Vector' />
                <Svg id='Vector' />
                <Svg id='Vector' />
                <Svg id='Vector' />
            </View>
            <View style={communityStyles.Rectangle11} />
            <Text style={communityStyles.No}>
                No
            </Text>
            <Text style={communityStyles.Title}>
                Title
            </Text>
            <Text style={communityStyles.Date}>
                Date
            </Text>
            <Text style={communityStyles.Nickname}>
                Nickname
            </Text>
            <Text style={communityStyles.Write}>
                Write
            </Text>
            <Text style={communityStyles.Count}>
                Count
            </Text>
            <Svg id='Vector1' />
            <View style={communityStyles['291']}>
                <Svg id='Vector' />
            </View>
            <View style={communityStyles.Heart1}>
                <Svg id='Vector' />

            </View>
            <View style={communityStyles.hearts}>
                <View style={communityStyles.Heart2}>
                    <Svg id='Vector' />

                    <Svg id='Vector' />

                    <Svg id='Vector' />
                    <Svg id='Vector' />
                    <Svg id='Vector' />
                    <Svg id='Vector' />
                    <Svg id='Vector' />
                    <Svg id='Vector' />
                    <Svg id='Vector' />
                    <Svg id='Vector' />
                    <Svg id='Vector' />
                    <Svg id='Vector' />
                    <Svg id='Vector' />
                </View>
            </View>
        </View>
    );
}

const communityStyles = StyleSheet.create({
    community: {
        width: 90,
        height: 64,
        backgroundColor: '#ffdf86',
    },
    commBox: {
        marginVertical: 12.5, // 수정
        marginHorizontal: 11.5, // 수정
        width: 65,
        height: 50,
    },
    Rectangle8: {
        width: 65,
        height: 50,
        backgroundColor: '#ffdede',
        borderColor: '#b2b7ff',
        borderWidth: 0.19,
    },
    Rectangle10: {
        marginVertical: 9.38, // 수정
        marginHorizontal: 6.94, // 수정
        width: 46.25,
        height: 37.5,
        backgroundColor: '#f5f5f5',
        borderColor: '#606579',
        borderWidth: 0.13,
    },
    JoinusLogin: {
        marginVertical: 1.5, // 수정
        marginHorizontal: 1.5, // 수정
        width: 5.31,
        height: 1.19,
        color: '#000000',
        fontFamily: 'Nunito, sans-serif',
        fontSize: 0.94,
        fontWeight: '600',
        lineHeight: 1.28,
    },
    SearchBar51: {
